title._content: Elliot, John Henry of Keene NH

description._content: TITLE Elliot, John Henry of Keene NH CREATOR SUBJECT Men - NH - Keene Business people, American - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION Photograph of John Henry Elliot of Keene New Hampshire. He was born in Keene in 1813 and graduated from Harvard in 1835. He married Emily Ann Wheelock in 1848 and they had 3 children. He was a director of the Cheshire railroad, president of the Cheshire bank, and in 1892 he gave the city the land and buildings for the Elliot Hospital. He died in 1895.
